### Problem Description

Synthetic source is wrong for arrays of flattened fields containing fields longer than ignore_above.

### Steps to Reproduce

```
PUT /my_index
{
  "mappings": {
    "_source": { "mode": "synthetic" },
    "properties": {
      "n": {
        "type": "flattened",
        "ignore_above": 4
      }
    }
  }
}

PUT my_index/_doc/1
{
  "n": [
    {
      "foo": "bar"
    },
    {
      "foo": "bazzzzzzz"
    }
  ]
}

GET my_index/_doc/1
```

Produces:
```
"_source": {
    "n": {
        "foo": "bazzzzzzz"
    }
}
```

